data.title: 1959 Press Photo New York Governor Nelson Rockefeller and his first wife
data.meta_description: This is an original press photo. They are living apart. The Rockefellers, married 31 years, have five grown children. They are shown in New York September 1959. Photo is dated 09--1959. It may contain wrinkles, cracks, and possibly even tears due to its age and how it was handled before it got to us.
